{"tid":1607630,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"網民發起放黑氣球 警紅磡帶走多人","createTime":"2019-10-01T02:04:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T10:17:46.000Z","uid":212626,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a69fd9a736bee0d6d8b8e31be67a38425ad2b5e1","tid":1607630,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:04:20.000Z","msg":"網民發起早上在尖沙咀星光大道一帶放黑氣球，警方在尖沙咀海傍戒備，截查多名市民。<br />\n<br />\n早上在紅磡海運軒對開的露天停車場，多名防暴警員截查一輛白色貨車。現場又有數個黑色氣球飄至暢通道行車天橋底部，消息指有十多人被帶走。尖東一帶亦有多名防暴警員巡邏，有警員截查附近車輛。<br />\n<br />\n防暴警員又在星光大道一帶截查部分身穿黑衣人士，有年輕人被要求將背包內的所有物品拿出來檢查。海面上亦有救護船在巡邏。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2264221/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2264221%2F&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdVT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=1db94a9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2264221/</a>"},{"pid":"7183d9231ab8c469f70d9edeae223e7c460a63c0","tid":1607630,"uid":290878,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:06:08.000Z","msg":"陳雲話你知，港島見，中共最驚人民有力量，團結即系力量，六區沒嗮力量，<br />\n<br />\n六區分化燃，六區不如返屋企訓教，甘驚，夠之後被共產化驚咩<br />\n<br />\n國慶日，popo夠膽燒槍，搶國慶頭版，講笑吧，最好來多次六四2.0,全世界都望住你，你就走不到，沒得狡辯"},{"pid":"74d92b652b6a58f7fee956ccc872371f5fef34ec","tid":1607630,"uid":167289,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7183d9231ab8c469f70d9edeae223e7c460a63c0","tid":1607630,"uid":290878,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:06:08.000Z","msg":"陳雲話你知，港島見，中共最驚人民有力量，團結即系力量，六區沒嗮力量，<br />\n<br />\n六區分化燃，六區不如返屋企訓教，甘驚，夠之後被共產化驚咩<br />\n<br />\n國慶日，popo夠膽燒槍，搶國慶頭版，講笑吧，最好來多次六四2.0,全世界都望住你，你就走不到，沒得狡辯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:08:49.000Z","msg":"陳雲：泛民害死人，要人去港島。外國善人收到可靠情報，明日香港會變成衙差統治，但疑是泛民的人依然號召義民去港島被圍捕。<br />\n泛民的人出來也許沒事（如果真的夠一百萬人出來反共而不是慶祝國慶），義民出去就會被打被殺被姦，之後泛民去美國領功。<br />\n外國人想救香港人，但香港人害死自己人。"},{"pid":"2b1021326178dfd8d409f858a00a6583b2dddde8","tid":1607630,"uid":70195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:11:14.000Z","msg":"個政權幾咁垃圾先會氣球都驚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92ac0d4aa20f858996cfd2686d54dc8fb23ca9fc","tid":1607630,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:18:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"368b1eabd5f2b1489e4ad6417c1e9d56e68eec4f","tid":1607630,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:20:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">六區開花要對準政權，梗係去議員辦事處賀佢老母啦</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好再</span></strong></span>企起街上面<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>圍警局</strong></span></span>，分區活動就應該<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>打游擊戰去搵該區既建制派議員</strong></span></span>同佢地開party一齊賀一賀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，至於邊一區去邊間就大家自己衡量下喇﹗<br />\n<br />\n屯門區區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdVT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=9d0fb477\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n荃灣區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdVT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=68c69c43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n沙田區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdVT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=eedd6cbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n黃大仙區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%99%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BB%2599%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdVT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=6aedd406\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%99%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n深水埗區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259F%2597%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdVT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=93fd472e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n灣仔區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%2581%25A3%25E4%25BB%2594%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdVT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=2d1cb6e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話（呢個係每日都可以做既）</span></span></strong><br />\n打電話搵議員(之前有巴打post過出黎，可以自己搵下)問下國慶期間區內有咩最新活動、巴士路線、有咩醫生診所好介紹呀等等，電話打唔通既whatsapp都可以，無whatsapp既巴絲打可以send email去，連email都無既可以fax過去查詢下，無人應既話可以搵下無限fax大法fax到佢應機為止。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>2.連儂牆</strong></span></span><br />\n都係搵立法會議員/區議員辦事處啦，無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>3.裝修</strong></span></span><br />\n有好多議員都扎根起屋邨做左好耐，裡面啲裝修又殘又舊，有心既手足可以襯國慶幫佢地補下油、翻新下添置返少少國慶節日既氣氛，用咩色就自己決定啦。<br />\n補充:好多office既出入口好窄，大家入office查詢既時候動作唔好太大呀，唔小心撞到佢地d玻璃就大鑊喇。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>4.餵office既龜龜食野(蟲系魔法師出動)</strong></span></span><br />\n巴絲打們都可以準備少少紅蟲、蚯蚓、生雞蛋、甜野呀個d比入面既龜龜食，可以吸引到更多蟲蟲輕易大量繁殖既就更好。大家知啦，議員們公事繁忙，萬一無時間餵佢地，龜龜都仲有少少野食丫嘛。<br />\n補充：拉開櫃桶餵既時候記住小心啲，唔好倒瀉手上罐可樂呀，會惹到成地蟻架！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>原post:</strong></span><br />\n國慶咁大件事 緊係要約埋建制議員賀佢老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1605409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1605409</a>"},{"pid":"e00f5378bf4736bba70821bbf417df4f2e691813","tid":1607630,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:20:59.000Z","msg":"尖沙咀要人！"},{"pid":"6bb48748c96642610df02042be5e28cc337784fd","tid":1607630,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:21:30.000Z","msg":"告唔到咩  係要48<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03984dd0633cc2ac4c91ce5c10b4f30827d0adc4","tid":1607630,"uid":185057,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"74d92b652b6a58f7fee956ccc872371f5fef34ec","tid":1607630,"uid":167289,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7183d9231ab8c469f70d9edeae223e7c460a63c0","tid":1607630,"uid":290878,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:06:08.000Z","msg":"陳雲話你知，港島見，中共最驚人民有力量，團結即系力量，六區沒嗮力量，<br />\n<br />\n六區分化燃，六區不如返屋企訓教，甘驚，夠之後被共產化驚咩<br />\n<br />\n國慶日，popo夠膽燒槍，搶國慶頭版，講笑吧，最好來多